## Code Organization

### File Structure

```javascript
// 1. Imports
import { CONFIG } from './config.js';
import { EventBus } from './EventBus.js';

// 2. Constants
const LOCAL_CONSTANT = 10;

// 3. Main class/functions
class MyComponent {
  // Properties first
  constructor() { }
  
  // Public methods
  publicMethod() { }
  
  // Private methods (prefixed with _)
  _privateMethod() { }
}

// 4. Exports
export { MyComponent };
```

### Function Order

Within a class:
1. Constructor
2. Public methods (alphabetically)
3. Private methods (alphabetically)
4. Getters/setters at the end

