## Code Review Checklist

### Before Submitting/Committing

- [ ] Code follows naming conventions
- [ ] No files exceed 400 lines
- [ ] No functions exceed 50 lines
- [ ] Magic numbers explained or in config
- [ ] Error handling is explicit
- [ ] Code tested and working
- [ ] No console.logs (except intentional logging)
- [ ] No commented-out code
- [ ] Architecture docs updated if structure changed (see `docs/architecture/README.md`)

