## Common Code Smells

### Detect and Refactor

🚩 **Duplicate code** → Extract shared function
```javascript
// ❌ Duplicate logic
function updatePlayer() { /* repeated code */ }
function updateEnemy() { /* same repeated code */ }

// ✅ Extract shared
function updateEntity(entity) { /* shared logic */ }
```

🚩 **Long parameter lists** → Use config object
```javascript
// ❌ Too many parameters
function createEntity(x, y, health, speed, sprite, size, color) { }

// ✅ Config object
function createEntity(config) {
  const { x, y, health, speed, sprite, size, color } = config;
}
```

🚩 **Deep nesting** → Use early returns
```javascript
// ❌ Deep nesting
if (a) {
  if (b) {
    if (c) {
      // do thing
    }
  }
}

// ✅ Early returns
if (!a) return;
if (!b) return;
if (!c) return;
// do thing
```

🚩 **God classes** → Split by responsibility
```javascript
// ❌ Renderer does everything (4000 lines!)
class Renderer {
  renderText() { }
  renderShapes() { }
  renderSprites() { }
  renderEffects() { }
  renderUI() { }
  renderDebug() { }
}

// ✅ Split by purpose
class TextRenderer { }
class ShapeRenderer { }
class SpriteRenderer { }
// etc.
```

